Aspen Kartier Banned From Twitch After Dog Abuse Backlash ğŸ˜³

Aspen Kartier banned from Twitch after dog abuse backlash is currently trending after a disturbing livestream clip went viral on January 29, 2026. This Aspen Kartier banned from Twitch after dog abuse backlash update details the moment viewers were left in shock when audio of repeated yelping was heard during a live broadcast.
In the viral clip, the rapper-turned-streamer is heard asking her dog how it escaped its cage before a series of thumping sounds and distressing yelps follow, leading many to believe the animal was being struck. The footage ends with Aspen carrying the dog out of the room by its scruff. Following an immediate and massive outcry from the community and animal rights advocates, Twitch has officially issued an indefinite ban on her account, which had over 70,000 followers. While Aspen has yet to release a full formal statement, the "Queen of the South" artist is facing a wave of de-platforming calls across YouTube and TikTok.

title: It's Happening! Modiâ€™s Huge BULLET TRAIN Update in India! #shorts
description:
India is moving closer to launching its first high-speed bullet train, and officials have now given a target date. The Union Railway Minister has said that the countryâ€™s first bullet train service is expected to begin operations on August 15, 2027, which is Indiaâ€™s Independence Day. The initial section of the project will start running before the full route is completed, so passengers can experience high-speed travel earlier.

The train will operate on the Mumbaiâ€“Ahmedabad high-speed rail corridor, a major new rail line being built between Maharashtra and Gujarat. This corridor is around 508 kilometres long, and the bullet trains on it are designed to travel at speeds of up to around 300â€“320 km/h, cutting travel time drastically compared with regular trains. The first phase may begin with a shorter segment between places like Surat and Bilimora or Vapi, with more sections opening in stages over time.

The full Mumbaiâ€“Ahmedabad route is expected to be completed by 2029, but the government is aiming to have the first operational stretch ready by mid-2027. This would mark a historic moment for Indian rail travel and introduce true high-speed services in the country for the first time.

title: The Quiet Wedding Dress That Became Iconic | Julie Andrews â€“ The Sound of Music (1965)
description:
This is one of the most understated wedding dresses in film history â€” and thatâ€™s exactly why it became unforgettable.
Worn by Julie Andrews as Maria in The Sound of Music (1965), this ivory silk shantung gown was designed by legendary costume designer Dorothy Jeakins.
With its high collar, long fitted sleeves, fabric-covered buttons, and soft A-line train, the dress reflects Mariaâ€™s journey from novitiate to bride â€” quiet, graceful, and deeply intentional.
No sparkle. No excess. Just craftsmanship, structure, and timeless elegance.
Even though the gown leans more toward 1950s bridal style than the filmâ€™s 1930s setting, it remains one of the most beloved wedding dresses in cinema history.

These were 23-year-old Sahil Dhaneshraâ€™s dreams, which he saw for himself and his mother.

But just when he was within touching distance of those dreams, his journey was cut short.

Sahil lost his life after a speeding Scorpio SUV rammed into his motorcycle. The SUV was being driven by a 17-year-old.

Sahil was found dead on the road when the police reached the spot. 

Peek TV spoke to his mother, Inna, a single parent who had faced countless hardships to raise her son. But now she is trying to find a reason to keep going.

The minor in the case has been granted bail, and his father has still not been arrested despite an FIR against him, raising questions of the law bending before power and privilege.

description:
Sattu Paratha with a special tangy twist! This recipe, inspired by Purav Jha, is simple, hearty, and full of flavor. But what takes it to the next level? Mango Pickle (Aachaar)! ğŸ¥­

Ingredients:

For the Dough:

2 cups Whole Wheat Flour

Water (for kneading)

Salt to taste

1 tbsp Oil

For the Sattu Stuffing:

1 cup Sattu (Roasted Gram Flour)

1 small Onion (finely chopped)

2-3 Green Chilies (finely chopped)

1 inch Ginger (grated) (optional)

1 tsp Amchur (Dry Mango Powder) or 2 tbsp Mango Pickle (finely chopped) ğŸ¥­

Â½ tsp Ajwain (Carom Seeds)

Â½ tsp Jeera (Cumin Seeds)

1 tbsp Mustard Oil

Salt to taste

Method:

Knead the Dough: Mix flour and salt. Add water gradually and knead into a soft dough. Add oil and knead again. Cover and rest for 15-20 minutes.

Prepare the Stuffing: In a bowl, mix sattu, onion, green chilies, ginger, coriander,  mango pickle, amchur, ajwain, jeera, and salt. Add mustard oil and mix well.

Assemble: Take a ball of dough, flatten it, and stuff it with a generous amount of the sattu-pickle mixture. Seal the edges and roll it out gently.

Cook: Heat a tawa. Cook the paratha on both sides, applying ghee or oil until golden brown spots appear.

Serve: Serve hot with extra pickle on the side and a glass of chaach!

title: Basant in Lahore | Section 144 enforced in Lahore to prevent â€˜politicisationâ€™ of Basant festival
description:
#Samaatv #SamaaNews #PakistanNews #Basant #Punjab #Kite 

Basant in Lahore | Section 144 enforced in Lahore to prevent â€˜politicisationâ€™ of Basant festival 
The Lahore district administration has imposed Section 144 to ensure the peaceful and safe celebration of the traditional Basant festival, banning kites carrying religious, political or national symbols to prevent any untoward incident.
According to an official notification, the preparation, sale, purchase and use of kites featuring images of holy books, religious sites, personalities, political parties or national flags have been strictly prohibited to maintain religious harmony and law and order during the festival.

The ban, imposed for 30 days under Section 144, applies to all forms of kites carrying religious or political prints. However, authorities clarified that the flying of plain single or multicolour kites without any images or symbols will be allowed during Basant.

The notification further stated that the manufacturing, storage, sale or use of illegal kites will be treated as a punishable offence, and strict legal action will be taken against violators.

Sources said the decision was taken amid concerns that miscreants could exploit the festival by using religious or political symbols, potentially disturbing public order.

Section 144 has come into force with immediate effect, and law enforcement agencies have been directed to ensure strict implementation of the restrictions.

Meanwhile, the Punjab government has granted conditional permission to celebrate a â€œsecured Basantâ€ from February 6 to 8. Deputy Commissioner Lahore has issued the Basant 2026 notification under the recently enacted Punjab Kite-Flying Act 2025, passed by the Punjab Assembly.

To enhance public safety, authorities have also planned additional precautionary measures, including the installation of safety nets and wire-protection systems on major roads to prevent accidents. Officials have reiterated that Basant celebrations will be allowed only under strict safety compliance, aiming to create a safe and festive environment for residents of Lahore.

title: Iconic Aeroplane Restaurant Shuts Down Permanently #news #delhi
description: The Flight of Dreams in Gurugram has permanently closed its doors, leaving many in the city shocked and disappointed. This iconic aeroplane restaurant, located in the heart of Gurgaon, Haryana, was a popular spot for locals and tourists alike, offering a unique dining experience. As part of the Kingdom of Dreams, it was a major attraction in the Delhi NCR region, and its closure is a significant change in the local news landscape. The time changing hands of ownership and management have ultimately led to its demise, and the people of Gurugram are mourning the loss of this beloved landmark. For those who have visited the Flight of Dreams, it was more than just a restaurant - it was an experience that will be deeply missed. Stay tuned for more updates on this developing story, and get the latest news on what's happening in Gurugram, including the best shorts and insights into Gurugram life. Ingredients:

For Gole:

1/2 cup besan/chickpea flour
7-8 garlic cloves
1/2 inch ginger
curry leaves
1 green chilli
salt as per taste
1/2 tsp coriander powder
1/2 tsp cumin powder
1/4 tsp turmeric powder
1/2 tsp red chilli powder
pinch of hing
2 spoon curd
3 spoon oil

For Rice:

1/2 cup basmati rice
1 + 1/4 cup water
pinch of turmeric
pinch of hing
1 tsp oil
1/2 lemon juice
salt as per taste

For Kadhi

1 cup curd
water as required
2 spoon besan
1 tbsn oil
1/2 tsp mustard seeds
few fenugreek seeds
pinch of turmeric
pinch of hing
green chilli
chopped garlic and ginger
coriander leaves

title: alasan orca di akuarium diberi es batu? #orca #hewan #rpuldunia
description:
pemberian es batu pada orka di akuarium bukan tanpa alasan. es batu bisa membantu orka memenuhi kebutuhan cairan tubuhnya. di alam liar orka tidak minum air secara langsung, sebagian besar cairan tubuh mereka didapat dari makanan.
Jika langsung diberi air tawar, orka justru bisa salah mengenalinya sebagai air laut dan otomatis akan menolak.
Di habitat aslinya, orka hidup di perairan yang sangat dingin. sementara suhu air di akuarium cenderung lebih hangat. Ditambah lagi, tubuh orka dilapisi lapisan lemak yang sangat tebal, sehingga panas tubuh menjadi sulit dilepaskan.
Karena itu, es batu menjadi solusi yang paling masuk akal. selain membantu menurunkan suhu tubuh, cara ini juga membantu memenuhi kebutuhan cairan orca secara aman dan alami.
